20that%20goods%20and%20service%20spending%20will%20be%20on%20a%20flat%20to%20downward%20trajectory%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E4.%20Clouds%20are%20forming%20after%20capex%20surge.%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20percentage%20of%20small%20businesses%20that%20view%20now%20as%20a%20bad%20time%20to%20expand%20due%20to%20higher%20interest%20rates%20is%20near%20the%20highest%20level%20on%20record...%20the%20composite%20of%20capex%20plans%20in%20the%20regional%20Fed%20Manufacturing%20surveys%20remains%20near%20the%20lowest%20level%20since%202009%20(excluding%20COVID%20periods)...%20only%2022%25%20of%20CEOs%20plan%20to%20increase%20their%20capex%20budgets%20over%20the%20next%2012%20months%E2%80%94the%20lowest%20level%20since%202020%2C%26quot%3B%20Adam%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20sour%20sentiment%20suggests%20capex%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20challenged%20going%20forward.%20And%20this%20has%20already%20started%20to%20translate%20into%20weaker%20demand%20for%20loans%2C%20as%20the%20net%20percentage%20of%20banks%20reporting%20stronger%20demand%20for%20loans%20has%20fallen%20to%20its%20lowest%20level%20since%202009.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftaylor-swift-eras-tour-economy-outlook-us-recession-consumer-spending-2023-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692022276000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64417bcf3f6f690018deb6a5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftaylor-swift-eras-tour-economy-outlook-us-recession-consumer-spending-2023-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BThe%20short-term%20economic%20boost%20from%20Taylor%20Swift's%20'Eras%20Tour'%C2%A0is%20ending%20as%20it%20moves%20overseas%2C%26quot%3B%20Raymond%20James%20said%20about%20worrying%20economic%20signs.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mfox%40businessinsider.com%20(Matthew%20Fox)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0