0seven-year-long%20anti-NEET%20struggle%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20CM%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20eve%20of%20Independence%20Day%2C%20the%20deaths%20by%20suicide%20of%20a%20student%2C%20Jagatheeswaran%2C%20who%20desired%20to%20pursue%20an%20MBBS%20course%20after%20clearing%20NEET%2C%20and%20his%20father%20Selvasekhar%20led%20to%20a%20question%3B%20Mr%20Stalin%20demanded%20to%20know%20if%20the%20freedom%20bestowed%20on%20the%20people%20is%20meant%20for%20all%20or%20whether%20it%20is%20only%20for%20a%20few%20rich%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BStarting%20from%20Anitha%20(Ariyalur%20District)%2C%20many%20invaluable%20lives%20(of%20aspirants)%20were%20lost%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20due%20to%20the%20NEET%20exam%20method...%20Our%20conscience%20is%20shaken%20by%20the%20moral%20questions%20raised%20by%20their%20deaths%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Ravi%20is%20callously%20making%20pro-NEET%20comments%20without%20realising%20how%20students%20from%20poor%2C%20ordinary%20and%20middle-class%20backgrounds%20are%20losing%20good%20opportunities%20due%20to%20that%20test.%20The%20Governor's%20activities%20appear%20to%20be%20indifferent%20to%20the%20student%20deaths%20due%20to%20NEET%2C%20the%20CM%20further%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Stalin%20said%20the%20DMK%20regime%20usually%20ignores%20Ravi's%20political%20comments%20on%20topics%20like%20those%20related%20to%20%26quot%3BAryan%20and%20Dravidian%26quot%3B%20and%20'Sanathanam'%20(Sanatana%20Dharma)%20as%20%26quot%3BAryan%20lament%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20if%20the%20Governor%20says%20that%20he%20would%20destroy%20marginalised%20people's%20dreams%20of%20pursuing%20a%20course%20in%20medicine%2C%20then%20%26quot%3Bwe%20consider%20it%20to%20be%20a%20conspiracy%20related%20to%20the%20education%20department.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chief%20minister%20said%20the%20future%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu%20students%20is%20important%20to%20the%20government.