20an%20uptick%20in%20sales.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20their%20sales%20picked%20up%2C%20Amanpreet%20also%20started%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F255951%2Fhyderabad-sids-farm-iit-kharagpur-cow-cattle-earns-crores-milk-subscription-plan-dairy-revenue-kishore-indukuri-inspirational-success-vid01%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etraining%20farmers%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20how%20to%20sell%20cow%20dung%20cakes%20and%20manure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThese%20farmers%20were%20dependent%20only%20on%20milk%20and%20were%20not%20given%20a%20good%20price%20for%20it.%20So%20we%20started%20training%20them%20on%20how%20to%20use%20the%20excreta%20from%20cows%2C%20make%20proper%20manure%2C%20and%20sell%20it.%20We%20trained%20over%2055%20farmers%2C%20mostly%20women%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Amanpreet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20help%20farmers%20get%20a%20daily%20income%20by%20selling%20cow%20dung%20cakes%20and%20manure.%20Female%20farmers%20are%20able%20to%20get%20Rs%20200-300%20per%20day%20sitting%20at%20home%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E70%25%20of%20electricity%20is%20generated%20on%20the%20farm%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201080px)%20100vw%2C%201080px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fgauu-1692019972.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Gau%20Organics%20sell%20cow%20dung%20cakes%20and%20manure%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fgauu-1692019972.jpg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fgauu-1692019972-240x300.jpg%20240w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fgauu-1692019972-500x625.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fgauu-16