c%20%E2%80%93%20had%20led%20to%20mass%20layoffs%20and%20financial%20dislocation%2C%20the%20brunt%20of%20which%20is%20still%20being%20felt%20by%20the%20country%2C%20especially%20its%20poor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20recent%20events%20we%20have%20witnessed%20in%20the%20country%2C%20and%20the%20more%20such%20that%20we%20may%20in%20the%20near%20future%2C%20are%20of%20an%20altogether%20different%20character%2C%20and%20indeed%20of%20a%20different%20order%20of%20things.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20strategic%20aim%20of%20their%20proponents%20is%20to%20overturn%20the%20constitutional%20state%20in%20India%20that%20took%20its%20rise%20in%20the%20democratic%20and%20non-violent%20movement%20helmed%20by%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20and%20the%20democratic%20polity%20it%20engendered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESteeped%20in%20it%2C%20and%20in%20part%20shaping%20it%20through%20his%20actions%20and%20writings%2C%20was%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%2C%20whose%20devotion%20to%20a%20liberal%20order%20of%20parliamentary%20democracy%2C%20and%20whose%20commitment%20to%20a%20free%20India%20for%20all%20Indians%20in%20a%20world%20freed%20of%20shackles%2C%20nurtured%20the%20Indian%20state%20upon%20independence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fthe-plot-to-kill-gandhi-was-a-manifestation-of-a-battle-for-the-soul-of-india%5C%22%3EThe%20Plot%20to%20Kill%20Gandhi%20Was%20a%20Manifestation%20of%20a%20Battle%20for%20the%20Soul%20of%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opponents%20of%20Gandhi%20and%20Nehru%20were%20communalist%20thinkers%20and%20actors%20of%20the%20pre-1947%20Muslim%20League%20and%20the%20Hindu%20Mahasabha%20of%20V.D.%20Savarkar%20and%20Nathuram%20Godse.%20Neither%20showed%20an%20interest%20in%20the%20ending%20of%20colonial%20rule.%20Their%20interest%20lay%20in%20creating%20and%20winning%20religious%20wars%20within.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20League%20under%20Muhammad%20Ali%20Jinnah%20succeeded%20in%20partitioning%20India%20with%20colonial%20encouragement%20and%20assistance.%20For%20all%20practical%20purposes%2C%20the%20Hindu%20Mahasabha%20folded%20up%20with%20the%20assassination%20of%20Gandhi%20by%20a%20man%20whose%20founding%20allegiance%20to%20the%20RSS%20had%20transferred%20itself%20to%20the%20Mahasabha%20under%20the%20inspiration%20of%20Savarkar%20without%20the%20severance%20of%20emotional%20links%20with%20the%20RSS%2C%20the%20fountainhead%20of%20the%20Hindu%20%3Cem%3Erashtra%3C%2Fem%3E%20thought.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20past%20ten%20years%2C%20the%20followers%20of%20the%20RSS%20have%20enjoyed%20practically%20untrammelled%20state%20power%20under%20the%20guardianship%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20and%20it%20is%20this%20which%20is%20now%20their%20aim%20to%20extend%20%E2%80%93%20at%20any%20price.%20Their%20immediate%20objective%20appears%20to%20be%20to%20prepare%20for%20an%20ideological%20seizure%20of%20India%20by%20the%20scruff%20of%20her%20neck.%20The%20ideas%20of%20Gandhi%20have%20to%20be%20rooted%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20beginning%20was%20made%20on%20August%2012%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fbuilding-of-gandhian-institute-in-varanasi-demolished%2Farticle67188305.ece%5C%22%3Eby%20bulldozing%20the%20structures%20of%20the%20Sarva%20Sewa%20Sangh%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Varanasi%2C%20the%20constituency%20of%20the%20prime%20minister%2C%20even%20as%20thousands%20stood%20to%20protest%20this%20wanton%20high-handedness%20imbued%20with%20communal%20hatred%20and%20hatred%20of%20Gandhi%2C%20the%20man%20whose%20ideals%20mark%20the%20line%20of%20separation%20between%20a%20democratic%20India%20and%20a%20communal%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECommunal%20conflagrations%20have%20to%20be%20lit%20%E2%80%93%20as%20Nuh%20in%20Haryana%20showed.%20But%20Nuh%20underscores%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fharyana-violence-mewat-hate-and-provocative-videos%5C%22%3Ecareful%20preparation%3C%2Fa%3E%20since%20the%20start%20of%20the%20year%2C%20when%20Muslim%20cattle%20traders%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fground-report-how-junaid-and-nasir-were-killed-by-cow-vigilantes%5C%22%3Elynched%20and%20burnt%20to%20death%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20idea%20was%20to%20give%20birth%20to%20provocation%20and%20anger.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Manipur%2C%20the%20launch%20of%20open%20war%20against%20the%20tribal%20people%20and%20their%20(Christian)%20faith%20is%20the%20path%20that%20the%20idea%20of%20assertion%20of%20the%20Hindutva%20forces%20has%20taken.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBrutality%2C%20atrocities%2C%20and%20brazen%20disregard%20for%20human%20life%20and%20human%20values%20have%20scarred%20Manipur%2C%20but%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fpm-modis-speech-shifting-focus-from-manipur-violence-to-launching-a-diatribe-against-congress%5C%22%3Eneither%20condemnation%3C%2Fa%3E%20nor%20effective%20action%20has%20come%20from%20the%20highest%20authorities.%20The%20criminals%20roam%20free.%20Anyone%20who%20stands%20in%20the%20way%20of%20the%20project%20sanctified%20at%20the%20very%20top%20has%20to%20be%20rudely%20shoved%20aside.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fmanipur-and-mewat-on-reading-two-landscapes-of-social-suffering%5C%22%3EManipur%20and%20Mewat%3A%20On%20Reading%20Two%20Landscapes%20of%20Social%20Suffering%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20perception%20of%20danger%20comes%20from%20the%20zeal%20and%20the%20ideological%20clarity%20of%20the%20senior%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20and%20the%2026-party%20opposition%20coalition%20called%20INDIA%2C%20which%20was%20born%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20spectacular%20victory%20against%20the%20BJP%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fkarnataka-democracy-modi-shah%5C%22%3Ein%20a%20campaign%20led%20by%20Modi%20himself%20in%20Karnataka%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20his%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%2C%20Gandhi%20has%20become%20the%20focal%20point%20of%20the%20ideological%20combat%20in%20prospect%2C%20with%20the%20organisational%20underpinning%20of%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20INDIA%20bloc.%20The%20PM%E2%80%99s%20reply%20to%20the%20no-confidence%20motion%20debate%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20amply%20demonstrated%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PM%20refused%20to%20answer%20questions%20on%20Manipur.%20He%20mocked%20Gandhi%2C%20his%20mother%2C%20his%20name%2C%20his%20party%20and%20said%20boorish%2C%20un-funny%20things%20which%20excited%20mirth%20among%20his%20ministers%20and%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20vile%20show%20was%20over%2C%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20opposition%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Chowdhary%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnarendra-modi-parliament-speech-manipur%5C%22%3Ewas%20suspended%20from%20parliament%3C%2Fa%3E.%20His%20crime%3F%20He%20had%20asked%20why%20Narendra%20Modi%20had%20become%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Enirav%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%2C%20or%20silent%2C%20on%20Manipur.%20In%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20the%20senior%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20leader%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Faap-mp-raghav-chadha-suspended-from-rajya-sabha%2Farticle67183751.ece%5C%22%3ERaghav%20Chadha%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20been%20suspended.%20Remember%2C%20not%20long%20ago%2C%20through%20machinations%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20had%20been%20thrown%20out%20of%20parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20issue%20of%20August%2013%2C%20a%20contemporary%20journal%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3ESunday%20Guardian%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20not%20known%20to%20be%20critical%20of%20the%20regime%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fsundayguardianlive.com%2Fopinion%2Fparliaments-flying-kiss-to-manipur%5C%22%3Ehas%20this%20to%20say%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6after%20the%20end%20of%20the%20no-confidence%20motion%2C%20an%20impression%2C%20rightly%20or%20wrongly%2C%20was%20created%20that%20the%20Indian%20parliament%20had%20given%20a%20flying%20kiss%20to%20Manipur.%20The%20treasury%20benches%20seemed%20determined%20to%20intimidate%20the%20opposition.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20India%20is%20not%20yet%20a%20Hindu%20rashtra%2C%20although%20forces%20to%20reach%20that%20goal%20have%20been%20unleashed%2C%20there%20is%20no%20getting%20away%20from%20the%20election%20process%20for%20now%2C%20even%20if%20this%20is%20rendered%20a%20sham%20through%20a%20manipulated%20Election%20Commission%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fnew-bill-selection-of-election-commissioners%5C%22%3Eas%20a%20new%20move%20of%20the%20government%3C%2Fa%3E%20would%20appear%20to%20suggest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThus%2C%20the%20route%20through%20which%20the%20Modi%20establishment%20will%20seek%20to%20exert%20its%20will%20seems%20to%20lie%20through%20elections%20in%20the%20first%20instance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fbjp-hindutva-karnataka-election%5C%22%3EWhy%20the%20BJP%20Won%E2%80%99t%20%E2%80%93%20and%20Can%E2%80%99t%20%E2%80%93%20Give%20Up%20on%20Hindutva%20as%20an%20Electoral%20Strategy%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPerhaps%20the%20regime%20calculates%20that%20if%20it%20is%20able%20to%20divide%20or%20polarise%20public%20opinion%20on%20religious%20lines%20to%20the%20extent%20that%20it%20can%20obtain%20the%20endorsement%20of%20roughly%20half%20the%20Hindu%20voters%2C%20then%20it%20may%20be%20able%20to%20win%20approximately%20more%20than%2040%25%20of%20the%20national%20vote%20in%20the%20next%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20(as%20against%2037.4%25%20in%202019).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvery%20single%20ugly%20event%20of%20a%20communal%20nature%20that%20happens%20or%20is%20made%20to%20happen%20these%20days%20flows%20from%20this%20imagination.%20Planned%20violence%20appears%20to%20fill%20the%20Hindutva%20followers%20with%20pride%20and%20faith%20in%20the%20capacities%20of%20the%20present%20dispensation%20%E2%80%93%20or%20at%20least%20this%20seems%20to%20be%20the%20thinking%20in%20powerful%20sections%20of%20the%20establishment%20and%20their%20adherents.%20There%20is%20no%20serendipity%20here%2C%20only%20plotting%20and%20calculation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20vote%20goal%20can%20be%20secured%2C%20the%20position%20of%20the%20current%20rulers%20will%20become%20unassailable%20in%20the%20next%20parliament%2C%20and%20a%20Modi%20Mark%20III%20government%20can%20be%20formed%20with%20the%20project%20of%20firming%20up%20a%20Hindu%20rashtra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShould%20that%20come%20to%20pass%2C%20laws%20in%20the%20direction%20of%20establishing%20a%20Hindu%20state%20can%20be%20worked%20upon%20even%20as%20armed%20social%20gangs%20are%20entrenched%20as%20a%20regular%20feature%20with%20close%20links%20to%20the%20police%20system%20and%20the%20administration%2C%20as%20already%20appears%20to%20be%20the%20case%20in%20BJP-run%20states%2C%20notably%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20Haryana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20striking%20emblem%20in%20these%20states%20of%20the%20Indian%20Union%20is%20the%20so-called%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftag%2Fbulldozer-politics%5C%22%3Ebulldozer%20justice%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20in%20which%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fopinion%2Flead%2Fdemolitions-as-state-sanctioned-collective-punishment%2Farticle67180107.ece%5C%22%3Eadministration%20is%20complicit%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20lower%20judiciary%20too%20frightened%20to%20act.%20The%20constitutional%20state%20has%20capitulated.%20The%20effective%20declaration%20of%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20principal%20religious%20minority%20as%20second-class%20citizens%20has%20occurred.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%