e%20injured%20stars%20could%20prepare%20themselves%20for%20the%20continental%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20a%20have%20few%20guys%20coming%20back%20from%20injuries%20in%20any%20case.%20We%20have%20to%20give%20them%20opportunities%20to%20play%20(in%20Asia%20Cup).%20We%20have%20a%20one%20week%20camp%20in%20Bengaluru%20from%20August%2023%20for%20the%20Asia%20Cup.%20We%20will%20take%20it%20as%20it%20comes%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20likes%20of%20Tilak%20Varma%2C%20Yashasvi%20Jaiswal%20and%20Mukesh%20Kumar%20made%20their%20debuts%20in%20the%20T20I%20series%20against%20West%20Indies%20and%20Dravid%20was%20quite%20impressed%20by%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20thought%20all%20the%20three%20guys%20who%20made%20debuts%20for%20us%20in%20this%20series%2C%20stood%20up.%20Yashasvi%20Jasiwal%20in%20the%20fourth%20game%2C%20I%20thought%20he%20played%20a%20very%20good%20innings.%20He's%20shown%20us%20what%20he%20can%20do%20in%20the%20IPL%20and%20it%20was%20nice%20to%20see%20him%20replicate%20that%20in%20international%20cricket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTilak%20Varma%2C%20I%20thought%2C%20was%20really%20good%2C%20to%20come%20in%20in%20the%20middle%20order.%20He%20came%20in%20sometimes%20in%20very%20difficult%20situations.%20But%20every%20time%2C%20he%20plays%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20intent%2C%20plays%20very%20positively%2C%20looks%20to%20move%20the%20game%20along%2C%20fielded%20brilliantly%20throughout%20the%20series%2C%20showed%20us%20he%20can%20bowl%20one%20or%20two%20overs%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20really%20positive%20signs%20from%20Tilak%20and%20to%20have%20that%20left-hander%20in%20the%20middle%20order%20does%20make%20a%20huge%20difference%20against%20some%20of%20the%20attacks%20that%20we've%20been%20playing%20against.%26quot%3B%20Prior%20to%20his%20T20%20debut%2C%20Mukesh%20also%20played%20his%20first%20game%20for%20India%20in%20the%20Test%20and%2050-over%20format.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20debuted%20in%20all%20the%20formats%20in%20this%20series%20and%20I%20thought%20he%20acquitted%20himself%20really%20well.%20His%20ability%20to%20bowl%20at%20the%20death%2C%20sometimes%20he%20was%20called%20upon%20to%20bowl%20against%20some%20really%20big%20powerful%20hard%20hitters%20and%20he%20acquitted%20himself%20well%20for%20someone%20who%20was%20just%20playing%20his%20fourth%20or%20fifth%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20I%20think%20there's%20some%20real%20good%20positives%20in%20the%20guys%20who%20made%20their%20debuts%20for%20us%20and%20hopefully%20they%20take%20confidence%20from%20the%20series%20and%20keep%20learning%20as%20they%20go%20forward.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692017760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2F1cn7qrvo_kl-rahul-and-shreyas-iyer_625x300_14_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fasia-cup%2Fkl-rahul-shreyas-iyer-to-return-for-asia-cup-indian-cricket-team-coach-rahul-dravid-drops-big-hint-4295923%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Both%20KL%20Rahul%20and%20Shreyas%20Iyer%20could%20be%20given%20the%20nod%20to%20play%20in%20the%20Asia%20Cup.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A39%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fasia-cup%2Fkl-rahul-shreyas-iyer-to-return-for-asia-cup-indian-cricket-team-coach-rahul-dravid-drops-big-hint-4295923%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fasia-cup%2Fkl-rahul-shreyas-iyer-to-return-for-asia-cup-indian-cricket-team-coach-rahul-dravid-drops-big-hint-4295923%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fasia-cup%2Fkl-rahul-shreyas-iyer-to-return-for-asia-cup-indian-cricket-team-coach-rahul-dravid-drops-big-hint-4295923%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Actor%20Shatrughan%20Sinha%20On%20Who%20He%20Would%20Like%20To%20See%20As%20PM%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EActor-turned-politician%20Shatrughan%20Sinha%20on%20Monday%20said%20he%20would%20love%20to%20see%20West%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20as%20the%20next%20Prime%20Minister%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Sinha%2C%20who%20is%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%2C%20headed%20by%20Ms%20Banerjee%2C%20made%20the%20statement%20in%20response%20to%20a%20query%20as%20to%20how%20he%20saw%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20as%20a%20prospective%20Prime%20Ministerial%20candidate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20would%20be%20very%20good%20for%20the%20country%20that%20at%20a%20time%20when%20we%20also%20have%20a%20woman%20as%20the%20President%2C%20we%20had%20a%20woman%20as%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20too.%20A%20firebrand%20leader%20like%20Mamata%20Banerjee%2C%20who%20has%20a%20mass%20base%2C%20would%20fit%20the%20bill%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20PTI%20in%20an%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Sinha%2C%20who%20represents%20Asansol%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20however%2C%20hastened%20to%20add%20%26quot%3Bwho%20would%20be%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20is%20a%20decision%20that%20would%20be%20taken%20at%20an%20appropriate%20time.%20My%20point%20is%20to%20underscore%20that%20we%2C%20in%20INDIA%2C%20have%20no%20dearth%20of%20talent.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20youth%20icon%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20in%20whom%20the%20nation%20sees%20its%20future.%20We%20have%20the%20modern%20day%20Chanakya%20-%20Sharad%20Pawar.%20And%20of%20course%2C%20we%20have%20firebrand%20mass%20leader%20Mamata%20Banerjee.%20In%20contrast%2C%20the%20BJP-led%20NDA%20has%20none%20except%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%26quot%3B%20asserted%20the%20actor-turned-politician.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Sinha%2C%20who%20quit%20the%20BJP%20four%20years%20ago%20and%20remained%20with%20the%20Congress%20for%20a%20brief%20period%20before%20joining%20the%20Trinamool%2C%20also%20asserted%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20does%20not%20behove%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20to%20mock%20our%20alliance%20with%20the%20use%20of%20terms%20like%20'ghamandia'%20(proud).%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20speaks%20of%20issues%20like%20corruption%20and%20nepotism%20to%20criticize%20the%20opposition%20coalition.%20As%20a%20former%20NDA%20insider%2C%20I%20wager%20that%20the%20BJP%20and%20its%20allies%20are%20second%20to%20none%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20nepotism.%20And%20their%20stand%20on%20corruption%20got%20exposed%20when%20they%20allied%20with%20those%20accused%20of%20corruption%20in%20Maharashtra%20by%20the%20PM%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Sinha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20flying%20kiss%20controversy%2C%20Mr%20Sinha%20said%20he%20was%20surprised%20at%20the%20allegation%20levelled%20against%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20by%20Union%20minister%20Smriti%20Irani%20%26quot%3Bwho%20respects%20me%20a%20lot%20as%20a%20senior%20in%20the%20acting%20profession%2C%20though%20unlike%20me%2C%20she%20never%20made%20it%20to%20films%20and%20remained%20confined%20to%20TV%20serials.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20too%20was%20present%20in%20the%20House%20at%20the%20time.%20No%20such%20gesture%20was%20made.%20I%20wonder%20why%20Irani%2C%20who%20has%20matured%20over%20the%20years%2C%20made%20such%20an%20allegation%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20superstar%20of%20yesteryears%2C%20adding%2C%20with%20a%20hint%20of%20mischief%2C%20the%20Urdu%20couplet%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3Ekuchh%20tho%20majbooriyan%20rahi%20hongi%2C%20yunhi%20koi%20bewafa%20nahin%20hota%20%3C%2Fem%3E(there%20must%20have%20been%20some%20pressing%20compulsions%2C%20one%20does%20not%20become%20unfaithful%20just%20like%20that)%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20Patna%20Sahib%20MP%2C%20who%20represented%20the%20seat%20covering%20his%20home%20town%20for%20two%20consecutive%20terms%2C%20until%20losing%20it%20in%202019%2C%20asserted%20that%20Bihar%20Chief%20Minister%20Nitish%20Kumar%20and%20his%20deputy%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%20were%20%26quot%3Babsolutely%20right%26quot%3B%20in%20taking%20exception%20to%20PM%20Modi's%20claim%20that%20a%20new%20AIIMS%20has%20been%20set%20up%20in%20Darbhanga.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20deplored%20PM%20Modi's%20'khooni%20khel'%20(game%20of%20blood)%20jibe%20at%20Ms%20Banerjee%20claiming%20it%20%26quot%3Bbetrayed%20the%20frustration%20over%20the%20thrashing%20received%20by%20the%20BJP%20in%20Panchayat%20polls%2C%20which%20saw%20the%20TMC%20registering%20a%20record%20win%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20adore%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20and%20call%20him%20didi%20(sister).%20What%20an%20ugly%20thing%20to%20say%20about%20her%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20country%20is%20gearing%20up%20for%20Raksha%20Bandhan%20festivities%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Sinha%20added%20with%20a%20rhetorical%20flourish.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692017640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-03%2Fi9kv6i3o_shatrughan-sinha-pti_625x300_14_March_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Factor-shatrughan-sinha-on-who-he-would-love-to-see-as-pm-4296520%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Actor-turned-politician%20Shatrughan%20Sinha%20on%20Monday%20said%20he%20would%20love%20to%20see%20West%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20as%20the%20next%20Prime%20Minister%20of%20the%20country.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Factor-shatrughan-sinha-on-who-he-would-love-to-see-as-pm-4296520%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Factor-shatrughan-sinha-on-who-he-would-love-to-see-as-pm-4296520%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Factor-shatrughan-sinha-on-who-he-would-love-to-see-as-pm-4296520%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Delhi%20Metro%20Station%20Gets%20Hoax%20Bomb%20Threat%2C%20Caller%20Arrested