ospital%20receives%2050%20to%20100%20very%2C%20very%20seriously%20wounded%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20hospital%20has%20so%20far%20treated%20about%2021%2C000%20soldiers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAmong%20these%2021%2C000%20soldiers%2C%202%2C000%20were%20missing%20limbs%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERussia%20has%20laid%20dense%20minefields%20across%20the%20east%20of%20Ukraine%2C%20which%20Ukraine%20says%20is%20hampering%20its%20counteroffensive%20efforts%20to%20take%20back%20territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20secretary%20of%20the%20country's%20National%20Security%20and%20Defense%20Council%2C%20Oleksiy%20Danilov%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdensity-russia-minefields-insane-says-ukraine-official-counteroffensive-2023-8%3Fr%3DUS%26IR%3DT%5C%22%3Ecalled%20the%20density%20of%20Russia's%20mines%20%26quot%3Binsane%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20earlier%20this%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20Ukraine's%20defense%20minister%2C%20Oleksii%20Reznikov%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fworld%2F2023%2Faug%2F13%2Fukraine-desperate-for-help-clearing-mines-says-defence-minister%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20The%20Guardian%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Ukraine%20was%20now%20the%20world's%20most%20heavily%20mined%20country.%20He%20asked%20the%20country's%20allies%20for%20more%20equipment%20to%20help%20clear%20the%20mines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20density%20of%20the%20minefields%20has%20forced%20Ukrainian%20soldiers%20in%20some%20places%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fminefields-force-ukraine-to-change-counteroffensive-strategy-russia-2023-7%5C%22%3Eget%20out%20of%20their%20Western-supplied%20tanks%20to%20try%20to%20advance%20on%20foot%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20while%20a%20shortage%20of%20advanced%20de-mining%20equipment%20has%20left%20some%20Ukrainians%20trying%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdensity-russia-minefields-insane-says-ukraine-official-counteroffensive-2023-8%3Fr%3DUS%26IR%3DT%5C%22%3Eclear%20mines%20by%20hand%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDoctors%20in%20Ukraine's%20southern%20region%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2023%2F08%2F02%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fukraine-war-casualties-wounded.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20The%20New%20York%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E%20earlier%20this%20month%20that%20they%20see%20many%20injuries%20caused%20by%20mines%20and%20shrapnel%20but%20few%20people%20hit%20by%20bullets%20during%20the%20current%20counteroffensive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20some%20cases%2C%20Ukrainian%20soldiers%20have%20been%20blasted%20by%20mines%20as%20they%20try%20to%20reach%20their%20comrades%20who%20were%20hit%20by%20other%20mines%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2023%2F07%2F16%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fukraine-russia-land-mines.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20Times%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkrainian%20soldiers%20also%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fi-didnt-realise-id-lost-my-leg-risks-taken-by-ukrainian-soldiers-to-diffuse-mines-and-booby-traps-12925979%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edescribed%20to%20Sky%20News%3C%2Fa%3E%20trying%20to%20locate%20mines%20with%20a%20metal%20detector%20while%20another%20soldier%20stood%20guard%20with%20an%20automatic%20weapon%2C%20all%20while%20Russian%20forces%20shelled%20and%20shot%20at%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EExperts%20previously%20told%20Insider%20that%20Russia%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnato-hesitation-giving-ukraine-weapons-hindering-counteroffensive-analysts-say-2023-6%3Fr%3DUS%26IR%3DT%5C%22%3Eable%20to%20build%20such%20strong%20defenses%2C%20including%20its%20minefields%2C%20because%20Western%20delays%20in%20sending%20Ukraine%20weapons%20postponed%20the%20start%20of%20its%20counteroffensive%20