le%20enjoying%20protection%20domestically.%20To%20the%20global%20community%2C%20Egyptian%20authorities%20are%20challenging%20the%20international%20system.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESeeking%20justice%20outside%20Egypt%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%2C%20the%20search%20for%20justice%20has%20moved%20into%20the%20international%20arena%20for%20the%20past%20decade.%20But%20even%20then%2C%20there%20hasn%E2%80%99t%C2%A0been%20much%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHuman%20rights%20organisations%20have%20called%20on%20the%20United%20Nations%20Human%20Rights%20Committee%20to%20investigate%20the%20massacre%2C%20but%20it%20has%20so%20far%20chosen%20not%20to.%20Egypt%20has%20not%20fully%20acceded%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20nofollow%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.african-court.org%2Fwpafc%2Fbasic-information%2F%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22External%20link%20%E2%80%94%20African%20Court%20on%20Human%20and%20Peoples'%20Rights%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAfrican%20Court%20on%20Human%20and%20Peoples%E2%80%99%20Rights%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%C2%A0judicial%20arm%20of%20the%20African%20Union.%20Nor%20is%20it%20a%20member%20of%20the%20International%20Criminal%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202014%2C%20Egyptian%20lawyers%20and%20the%20Freedom%20and%20Justice%20Party%2C%20to%20which%20deposed%20President%20Morsi%20belongs%2C%20asked%20the%20ICC%20to%20investigate%20alleged%20crimes%20against%20humanity%20at%20Rabaa.%20But%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20nofollow%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.icc-cpi.int%2Fnews%2Fdetermination-office-prosecutor-communication-received-relation-egypt%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22External%20link%20%E2%80%94%20ICC%20turned%20them%20down%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EICC%20turned%20them%20down%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20saying%20that%20those%20requesting%20the%20investigation%20were%20not%20legitimate%20representatives%20of%20the%20Egyptian%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%C2%A0a%20senior%20Egyptian%20military%20commander%2C%20Mahmoud%20Hegazy%2C%20visited%20an%20arms%20trade%20fair%20in%20the%20UK%20in%202015%2C%20lawyers%20acting%20for%20the%20Freedom%20and%20Justice%20Party%20asked%20British%20police%20to%20arrest%20him%20over%20allegations%20of%20torture%20and%20because%20he%20was%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20nofollow%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fworld%2F2015%2Fnov%2F02%2Fegyptian-opposition-legal-battle-uk-immunity-sisi-aide%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22External%20link%20%E2%80%94%20%26quot%3Bintegral%20to%20the%20dispersal%20plans%20in%20Rabaa.%26quot%3B%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9Cintegral%20to%20the%20dispersal%20plans%20in%20Rabaa.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0The%C2%A0police%20turned%20down%20the%20request%20because%20Hegazy%20had%20special%20diplomatic%20immunity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Findia-is-reaching-out-to-egypt-but-there-are-challenges-in-the-offing%5C%22%3EIndia%20Is%20Reaching%20Out%20to%20Egypt%20%E2%80%93%20But%20There%20Are%20Challenges%20in%20the%20Offing%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSo%20the%20only%20real%20options%20you%E2%80%99re%20left%20with%20are%20the%20sorts%20of%20inquiries%20by%20various%20United%20Nations%20bodies.%20Or%20universal%20jurisdiction%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Rupert%20Skilbeck%2C%20director%20of%20Redress%2C%20a%20London-based%20legal%20rights%20organisation%20that%20supports%20torture%20victims%20trying%20to%20obtain%20justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECould%20%E2%80%98universal%20jurisidiction%E2%80%99%20help%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20purest%20form%2C%20the%20legal%20principle%20of%20universal%20jurisdiction%20allows%20authorities%20in%20any%20country%20to%20prosecute%20individuals%20who%20have%20committed%20war%20crimes%20in%20any%20other%20country%2C%20regardless%20of%20whether%20they%20or%20their%20crimes%20have%20a%20connection%20to%20the%20prosecuting%20nation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20practice%20however%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fsyrians-seek-justice-for-war-crimes-in-europes-courts%2Fa-55632079%5C%22%3Eit%20is%20often%20watered%20down%20by%20various%20considerations%3C%2Fa%3E.%20These%20include%20whether%20there%20are%20witnesses%20in%20the%20prosecuting%20country%2C%20whether%20there%E2%80%99s%20any%20chance%20of%20arresting%20the%20alleged%20criminals%20and%20also%2C%20perhaps%20most%20importantly%2C%20whether%20local%20prosecutors%20want%20to%20take%20on%20the%20case.%20Often%20there%20are%20political%20aspects%20attached%20to%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20reality%20is%20that%20universal%20jurisdiction%20in%20this%20case%20would%20be%20quite%20difficult%2C%20because%20there%E2%80%99s%20no%20real%20possibility%20of%20extraditing%20senior%20people%20from%20Egypt%2C%E2%80%9D%20Skilbeck%20told%20%3Cem%3EDW%3C%2Fem%3E.%20%E2%80%9CAnd%20not%20many%20countries%20are%20prepared%20to%20do%20trials%20in%20absentia%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added%2C%20referring%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fegyptians-stand-trial-over-murder-of-italian-student-in-cairo%2Fa-59498732%5C%22%3Etrials%20conducted%20without%20a%20defendant%20in%20court%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20in%20Germany%2C%20recently%20described%20as%20a%20world%20leader%20in%20its%20use%20of%20universal%20jurisdiction%2C%20a%20case%20against%20Egyptian%20officials%20is%20unlikely.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirst%20of%20all%2C%20you%20would%20have%20to%20prove%20a%20crime%20against%20humanity%20had%20been%20committed%2C%20according%20to%20legal%20definitions%2C%20explained%20Andreas%20Sch%C3%BCller%2C%20director%20of%20the%20International%20Crimes%20and%20Accountability%20program%20at%20the%20Berlin-based%20European%20Center%20for%20Constitutional%20and%20Human%20Rights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20organisation%20was%20a%20prime%20mover%20behind%20Germany%E2%80%99s%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fgerman-court-finds-syrian-ex-colonel-guilty-of-crimes-against-humanity%2Fa-60407021%5C%22%3Erecent%20prosecution%20of%20Syrian%20war%20criminals%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0using%20universal%20jurisdiction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20far%20as%20I%20know%20there%20are%20no%20courts%20or%20other%20institutions%20that%20have%20made%20this%20finding.%20So%20you%E2%80%99d%20need%20to%20establish%20it%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20which%20requires%20a%20big%20effort%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sch%C3%BCller%20told%20%3Cem%3EDW%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22How%20to%20Indict%20Perpetrators%20%E2%80%93%20Nuremberg%E2%80%99s%20History%20Lessons%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fhow-to-indict-persecutors%5C%22%3EHow%20to%20Indict%20Perpetrators%20%E2%80%93%20Nuremberg%E2%80%99s%20History%20Lessons%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20against%20Syrian%20war%20criminals%20went%20ahead%20because%20of%20a%20confluence%20of%20factors%2C%20including%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fgerman-torture-trial-a-syrian-opposition-legend-speaks-out%2Fa-54727286%5C%22%3Ewitnesses%2C%20evidence%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%C2%A0perpetrators%20in%20Germany%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20political%20will.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20this%20is%20not%20like%20the%20Syrian%20case%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Sch%C3%BCller.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20were%20no%20diplomatic%20relations%20with%20the%20Syrian%20government.%20Egypt%20has%20a%20lot%20of%20political%20support%20internationally.%20It%20is%20also%20not%20a%20signatory%20to%20the%20relevant%20UN%20treaties%20or%20the%20ICC%E2%80%99s%20Rome%20Statute.%20So%20nobody%20is%20really%20willing%20to%20take%20these%20cases%2C%20which%20would%20also%20require%20a%20very%20targeted%20investigation%20and%20a%20certain%20constellation%20of%20factors%20to%20get%20it%20prosecuted.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20see%20this%20all%20the%20time%20in%20human%20rights%20work%2C%E2%80%9D%20added%20Redress%E2%80%99%20Skilbeck%2C%20%E2%80%9Cwhere%20certain%20Western%20countries%20will%20not%20take%20a%20firm%20stance%20against%20other%20countries%20because%20of%20the%20political%20situation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESch%C3%BCller%20also%20believes%20international%20interest%20has%20shifted%20to%20countries%20like%20Ukraine%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fsudan-over-3-million-displaced-by-conflict-un-says%2Fa-66201174%5C%22%3ESudan%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0or%20Iran.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EAmr%20Magdi%2C%20a%20senior%20researcher%20at%20Human%20Rights%20Watch%2C%20has%20similar%20opinions.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20political%20climate%20in%20the%20region%20has%20contributed%20to%20human%20rights%20violations%20in%20Egypt%20being%20overlooked%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20%3Cem%3EDW%3C%2Fem%3E.%20%E2%80%9CAt%20that%20time%2C%20the%20whole%20region%20was%20rife%20with%20problems%2C%20including%20civil%20war%20in%20Syria%2C%20Yemen%20and%20Libya.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20Egyptian%20government%20has%20managed%20to%20play%20on%20issues%20that%20concern%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20world%2C%20Magdi%20argued%2C%C2%A0%E2%80%9Cso%20that%20democracy%20and%20human%20rights%20are%20overlooked%20in%20exchange%20for%20Egypt%20taking%20care%20of%20European%20interests%2C%20such%20as%20combating%20irregular%20migration%2C%20security%20cooperation%20and%20economic%20relations.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EChanges%20in%20attitudes%20toward%C2%A0Egypt%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENevertheless%2C%20there%20may%20yet%20be%20some%20minimal%20hope%20that%20justice%20could%20one%20day%20be%20brought%20to%20bear%20on%20the%20Rabaa%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20lot%20of%20the%20legal%20decisions%20made%20about%20the%20case%20happened%20in%20the%20immediate%20afte