C%20the%20central%20bank%20plans%20to%20hire%20experts%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20September%20last%20year%2C%20the%20central%20bank%20had%20invited%20the%20expression%20of%20interest%20(EoI)%20from%20firms%20to%20be%20engaged%20as%20consultants%20to%20help%20RBI%20by%20generating%20supervisory%20inputs.%20Seven%20were%20shortlisted%20among%20the%20applicants%2C%20namely%20Accenture%20Solutions%20Private%20Limited%2C%20Boston%20Consulting%20Group%20(India)%20Pvt%20Ltd%2C%20Deloitte%20Touche%20Tohmatsu%20India%20LLP%2C%20Ernst%20and%20Young%20LLP%2C%20KPMG%20Assurance%20and%20Consulting%20Services%20LLP%2C%20McKinsey%20and%20Company%2C%20and%20Pricewaterhouse%20Coopers%20Pvt%20Ltd.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20the%20RBI%20has%20zeroed%20in%20on%20McKinsey%20and%20Company%2C%20and%20Accenture%20Solutions%20Private%20Limited.%20The%20project%20is%20set%20to%20cost%20Rs%2091%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20RBI%20has%20already%20been%20using%20AI%20and%20ML%20in%20its%20supervisory%20processes%2C%20it%20now%20intends%20to%20scale%20it%20up%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20benefits%20of%20advanced%20analytics%C2%A0can%20accrue%20to%20the%20Department%20of%20Supervision%20in%20the%20central%20bank.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20notification%20issued%20by%20the%20RBI%20in%20September%20last%20year%2C%20the%20Department%20of%20Supervision%20had%20already%20been%20developing%20and%20using%20linear%20and%20a%20few%20machine-learning%20models%20for%20supervisory%20examinations.%20But%2C%20it%20said%20the%20interest%20now%20is%20to%20explore%20the%20data%20to%20identify%20its%20attributes%20that%20can%20be%20leveraged%20to%20generate%20new%20and%20improved%20supervisory%20inputs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBanks%2C%20urban%20cooperative%20banks%2C%20NBFCs%2C%20payment%20banks%2C%20small%20finance%20banks%2C%20local%20area%20banks%2C%20credit%20information%20companies%2C%20and%20select%20all%20Indian%20financial%20institutions%20come%20under%20the%20supervisory%20ambit%20of%20the%20RBI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20its%20supervision%2C%20RBI%20assesses%20the%20financial%20soundness%2C%20solvency%2C%20asset%20quality%2C%20governance%20framework%2C%20liquidity%2C%20and%20operational%20viability%20of%20these%20institutions%20to%20save%20depositors%E2%80%99%20interests%20and%20financial%20stability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20RBI%2C%20in%20its%20EoI%20issued%20in%20September%20last%20year%2C%20had%20said%20regulatory%20and%20supervisory%20authorities%20around%20the%20globe%20are%20using%20machine%20learning%20techniques%20(commonly%20referred%20to%20as%20%E2%80%98suptech%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98regtech%E2%80%99)%20for%20assisting%20supervisory%20and%20regulatory%20activities.%20Although%20it%20said%2C%20most%20of%20these%20techniques%20are%20still%20exploratory%2C%20they%20are%20rapidly%20growing%20in%20popularity%20and%20scale.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20RBI%20notification%20further%20went%20on%20to%20say%20that%20AI%20and%20ML%20technologies%20are%20used%20for%20real-time%20data%20reporting%2C%20effective%20data%20management%2C%20and%20dissemination%20in%20terms%20of%20data%20collection.%20As%20for%20data%20analytics%2C%20it%20said%20they%20are%20being%20used%20for%20monitoring%20supervised%20firm-specific%20risks%2C%20including%20liquidity%20risks%2C%20market%20risks%2C%20credit%20exposures%20and%20concentration%20risks%2C%20misconduct%20analysis%2C%20and%20mis-selling%20of%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692010222000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F01%2Frbi_pti.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Frbi-to-use-ai-for-regulatory-supervision-awards-contract-to-mckinsey-and-accenture%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Although%20the%20RBI%20has%20already%20been%20using%20AI%20and%20machine%20learning%20in%20its%20supervisory%20processes%2C%20it%20now%20intends%20to%20scale%20it%20up%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20