he%20photo%2C%20Sunny%20seemed%20visibly%20irritated.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fgadar-2-star-sunny-deol-gets-angry-after-a-woman-tries-to-get-closer-to-him-see-photos%2Farticleshow%2F102721620.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Southern%20Anomaly%3A%20Decoding%20the%20Telugu%20Parties'%20Mixed%20Signals%20Towards%20the%20BJP%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F13123801%2FTelugu-leaders.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20May%2013%2C%20after%20the%20stupendous%20victory%20of%20the%20Siddaramaiah-Shivakumar%20Congress%20duo%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%20chief%20minister%20M.K.%20proudly%20tweeted%20that%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmkstalin%2Fstatus%2F1657316644400553993%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9Clandmass%20of%20%5Bthe%5D%20Dravidian%20family%20stands%20clear%20of%20%5Bthe%5D%20BJP%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20a%20proclamation%20full%20of%20hope%20and%20promise%20for%20India%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20nation%20faces%20an%20existential%20crisis.%20There%20have%20also%20been%20multiple%20commentaries%20since%20then%20about%20the%20chief%20ministers%20of%20Kerala%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%20and%20Karnataka%20upholding%20Dravidian%20values.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20other%20two%20major%20states%20in%20the%20south%20%E2%80%93%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20and%20Telangana%20%E2%80%93%20appear%20to%20be%20an%20anomaly%20to%20this%20model.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20Telugu%20states%20are%20also%20ruled%20by%20non-BJP%20governments%20but%20that%20seems%20to%20be%20the%20only%20thing%20that%20they%20share%20with%20the%20other%20southern%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20beginners%2C%20both%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20and%20Telangana%20have%20chief%20ministers%20(Y.S.%20Jaganmohan%20Reddy%20of%20the%20Yuvajana%20Sramika%20Rythu%20Congress%20Party%20(YSRCP)%20and%20K.%20Chandrasekhar%20Rao%20(KCR)%20of%20the%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%20(BRS)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Ftelangana%2FGhadis-fade-into-history-in-Telangana%2Farticle14477223.ece%5C%22%3Ewho%20hail%20from%20politically%20and%20economically%20well-off%20castes%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20Reddy%20and%20Velama%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20counterparts%20from%20opposition%20parties%20also%20belong%20to%20similarly%20well-entrenched%20castes%20%E2%80%93%20Kammas%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthesouthfirst.com%2Fbehind-the-news%2Fof-the-kamma-reddy-tdp-ysrcp-caste-rivalry-in-andhra-and-why-there-are-black-sheep-in-every-party%2F%5C%22%3E(founders%20of%20the%20Telugu%20Desam%20Party%20i.e.%20TDP)%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20again%20Reddys%20(who%20occupy%20top%20positions%20in%20the%20Congress%20party)%20in%20Telangana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20in%20stark%20contrast%20to%20Kerala%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%20and%20Karnataka%2C%20all%20of%20which%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fsiddaramaiah-counter-modi-communal-obc-politics%5C%22%3Enow%20helmed%20by%20OBC%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20backward%20class%2C%20chief%20ministers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20a%20testament%20to%20the%20devolution%20of%20power%20to%20more%20diverse%20sections%20of%20society%20in%20these%20three%20southern%20states%2C%20as%20opposed%20to%20the%20continued%20concentration%20of%20power%20within%20the%20wealthy%20castes%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20and%20Telangana%2C%20members%20of%20which%20have%20occupied%20the%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20post%20for%20the%20past%20seven%20decades%2C%20barring%20minor%20exceptions%20(including%20in%20the%20undivided%20Andhra%20Pradesh).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENaturally%2C%20there%20is%20no%20demand%20for%20a%20caste%20census%20in%20the%20Telugu%20states%20from%20the%20major%20parties.%20All%20the%20neighbouring%20chief%20ministers%20are%20now%20part%20of%20the%20INDIA%20(Indian%20National%20Developmental%20Inclusive%20Alliance)%20coalition%2C%20which%20has%20officially%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2F26-opposition-parties-joint-resolution-pitches-for-conducting-caste-census%2Farticle67094062.ece%5C%22%3Eadopted%20the%20demand%20for%20a%20caste%20census%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20exercise%20has%20been%20recognised%20as%20a%20necessity%20if%20there%20is%20ever%20to%20be%20a%20meaningful%20thrust%20towards%20an%20egalitarian%20society.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fwhy-the-bjp-is-afraid-of-a-caste-census%5C%22%3EWhy%20the%20BJP%20is%20Afraid%20of%20a%20Caste%20Census%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20national%20stage%20is%20being%20set%20for%20the%20parliamentary%20elections%20in%202024%2C%20regional%20parties%20from%20both%20the%20Telugu%20states%20are%20conspicuously%20absent%20from%20the%20INDIA%20coalition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20itself%2C%20the%20BJP%20is%20not%20expected%20to%20win%20any%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20and%20barely%20a%20few%20in%20Telangana.%20But%20it%20is%20believed%20that%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanchronicle.com%2Fnation%2Fpolitics%2F050723%2Fmixed-feelings-arise-with-return-of-bjp-moderates.html%5C%22%3EBJP%20is%20counting%20on%20this%20tacit%20support%20from%20all%20the%20regional%20parties%20in%20the%20Telugu%20states%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20compensate%20for%20projected%20losses%20elsewhere%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20time%20when%20the%20BJP%20is%20aggressively%20pushing%20its%20unabashed%20Hindutva%20agenda%2C%20political%20parties%20across%20the%20spectrum%20from%20the%20Telugu%20states%20seem%20to%20be%20insouciant%20in%20a%20way%20that%20makes%20one%20ponder%20if%20these%20rumours%20are%20true.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3