%20His%20articles%20are%20devoted%20towards%20voicing%20the%20concerns%20of%20downtrodden%20and%20marginalised%20communities.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692006626000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F13123801%2FTelugu-leaders.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftelugu-parties-bjp-mixed-signal-india-coalition%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Telugu%20states%20seem%20cut%20off%20from%20the%20model%20of%20anti-Hindutva%20politics%20prevailing%20in%20the%20other%20southern%20states.%20But%20could%20new%20momentum%20from%20the%20INDIA%20coalition%20change%20that%20in%20the%20months%20to%20come%3F%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftelugu-parties-bjp-mixed-signal-india-coalition%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22These%20Are%20Most%20Liveable%20Cities%20In%20Asia-Pacific.%20How%20Do%20Indian%20Cities%20Rank%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20global%20city%2C%20Singapore%20is%20no%20stranger%20to%20being%20on%20%E2%80%9Cbest%E2%80%9D%20lists.%C2%A0%20Recent%20accolades%20it%20has%20picked%20up%20include%20the%20country%20with%20the%20%E2%80%9Cbest%20business%20environment%E2%80%9D%20(EIU)%2C%20%E2%80%9Cfreest%20economy%20in%20the%20world%E2%80%9D%20(The%20Heritage%20Foundation)%2C%20fourth%20most%20competitive%20economy%20in%20the%20world%20(International%20Institute%20for%20Management%20Development)%2C%20and%20eighth%20place%20in%20Schroders's%20global%20city%20index.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETherefore%2C%20it%20was%20with%20little%20surprise%20that%20it%20did%20not%20make%20it%20into%20the%20top%20ten%20cities%20in%20the%20latest%20Economist%20Intelligence%20Unit%20(EIU)%20ranking%20of%20the%20most%20liveable%20cities%20in%20the%20world.%20The%20Southeast%20Asian%20city%20did%20however%20sneak%20into%20the%20top%20among%20Asia-Pacific%20cities%20in%20tenth%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20year's%20EIU%20liveability%20index%2C%20which%20provides%20a%20snapshot%20of%20the%20most%2C%20and%20least%2C%20desirable%20cities%20to%20live%20in%2C%20recorded%20the%20highest%20global%20average%20score%20in%2015%20years%2C%20showing%20that%20living%20conditions%20in%20cities%20across%20the%20world%20have%20fully%20recovered%20from%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20which%20disrupted%20lives%20and%20impacted%20lifestyles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20index%20rates%20living%20conditions%20in%20173%20cities%20across%20five%20categories%3A%20stability%2C%20healthcare%2C%20culture%20and%20environment%2C%20education%2C%20and%20infrastructure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20the%20categories%20covered%20by%20the%20survey%2C%20only%20the%20stability%20score%20dropped%20on%20average%20in%202023.%20Although%20stability%20scores%20in%20many%20eastern%20European%20cities%2C%20which%20fell%20in%202022%20because%20they%20are%20close%20to%20Ukraine%2C%20rose%20this%20year%2C%20stability%20deteriorated%20elsewhere.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStability%20scores%20were%20negatively%20affected%20by%20striking%20workers%20and%20protests%20in%20various%20European%20cities%20like%20Greece%20and%20France%20as%20well%20as%20deadly%20clashes%20in%20Israel%20and%20Peru.%20%C2%A0The%20EIU%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9Cinflation%20could%20lead%20to%20further%20falls%20in%20stability%20scores%2C%20and%20thus%20damage%20overall%20liveability%20scores%2C%20in%20many%20parts%20of%20the%20world%20over%20the%20next%20year.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20index%20revealed%20that%20cities%20in%20the%20Asia-Pacific%20region%20have%20rebounded%20the%20most%20with%20eight%20of%20the%20ten%20biggest%20upward%20movers%20coming%20from%20the%20region.%20New%20Zealand's%20Wellington%20rose%2035%20spots%20to%20take%2023rd%20place%2C%20while%20Auckland%20rose%2025%20places%20to%20land%20at%20number%2010.%20Hanoi%2C%20Vietnam%20moved%20up%2020%20places%20to%20129%2C%20whereas%20Kuala%20Lumpur%2C%20Malaysia%20jumped%2019%20positions.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPost-pandemic%20improvements%20in%20education%20and%20healthcare%20led%20to%20an%20improvement%20in%20scores%20across%20Asia.%20These%20two%20factors%20are%20also%20the%20main%20reason%20scores%20in%20Africa%20and%20the%20Middle%20East%20rose.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20EIU%20named%20Vienna%2C%20the%20%E2%80%9CCity%20of%20Music%E2%80%9D%2C%20also%20known%20as%20the%20%E2%80%9CCity%20of%20Dreams%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20most%20liveable%20city%20in%20the%20world%20for%20the%20fourth%20time%20in%20five%20years.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Economist%20report%20credited%20Vienna%20for%20its%20excellent%20mix%20of%20stability%2C%20culture%20and%20entertainment%2C%20and%20reliable%20infrastructure.%20Copenhagen%2C%20a%20similarly%20sized%20city%20with%20many%20of%20the%20same%20characteristics%2C%20is%20second.%20Melbourne%2C%20which%20regularly%20features%20among%20the%20top%20in%20the%20ranking%20came%20in%20third%20place.%20Fellow%20Aussie%20city%20Sydney%20is%20fourth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECanada%20has%20three%20cities%20in%20the%20top%20ten%20%E2%80%93%20Vancouver%20in%20fifth%2C%20Calgary%20in%207th%20and%20Toronto%20in%209th.%20The%20other%20cities%20that%20made%20it%20into%20the%20top%20ten%20are%20Zurich%20(6th)%2C%20Geneva%20(joint%207th)%2C%20Osaka%20(10th)%20and%20Auckland%20(joint%2010th).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20an%20expat%2C%20the%20downside%20of%20living%20in%20these%20cities%20is%20that%20you%20should%20not%20expect%20to%20receive%20any%20form%20of%20%E2%80%9Chardship%E2%80%9D%20compensation.%20The%20liveability%20survey%20was%20designed%20by%20the%20EIU%20to%20help%20companies%20calculate%20hardship%20allowances%20for%20staff%20who%20were%20moving%20to%20a%20new%20and%20possibly%20less%20tolerable%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20all%2C%20nine%20of%20the%20top%20ten%20cities%20are%20small%20to%20mid-sized.%20All%20ten%2C%20and%20indeed%20most%20of%20the%20top%2050%2C%20are%20in%20rich%20countries.%20Big%20cities%20with%20high%20levels%20of%20crime%2C%20congestion%20and%20density%20tend%20to%20fare%20less%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20the%2010%20cities%20to%20slip%20farthest%20down%20the%20rankings%2C%20three%20were%20in%20the%20UK%20%E2%80%94%20Edinburgh%2C%20Manchester%20and%20London%20%E2%80%94%20and%20two%20in%20the%20US%2C%20Los%20Angeles%20and%20San%20Diego.%20London%20fell%2012%20places%20from%20a%20year%20ago%20to%2046th%20and%20New%20York%20tumbled%20ten%20spots%20to%2069th.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20Chinese%20cities%20were%20%E2%80%9Cbroadly%20stable%20when%20compared%20to%20last%20year's%20results%2C%E2%80%9D%20according%20to%20the%20survey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20four%20Indian%20cities%20in%20the%20study%2C%20New%20Delhi%2C%20Mumbai%2C%20Chennai%20and%20Bangalore%2C%20are%20ranked%20between%20positions%2045%20and%2050%20among%20Asia-Pacific%20cities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Asia-Pacific%20region%2C%20Karachi%2C%20Port%20Moresby%20(Papua%20New%20Guinea)%20and%20Dhaka%20are%20the%20three%20least%20desirable%20cities%20to%20live%20in.%20In%20the%20global%20rank%2C%20they%20are%20in%20positions%20169%2C%20168%2C%20and%20167%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20global%20table%2C%20Damascus%20took%20the%20dubious%20honour%20of%20the%20least%20liveable%20city%20in%20the%20world.%20It%20has%20held%20this%20place%20in%20the%20index%20for%20more%20than%20ten%20years.%20Tripoli%20is%20one%20space%20above%20in%20172%2C%20although%20its%20score%20is%20nearly%20ten%20points%20higher%20than%20that%20of%20Syria's%20war-ravaged%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKyiv%2C%20despite%20its%20efforts%20to%20protect%20itself%20from%20the%20war%2C%20also%20features%20in%20the%20bottom%20ten.%20It%20was%20excluded%20from%20the%20index%20in%202022%20because%20Russia%20invaded%20Ukraine%20while%20the%20data%20were%20being%20collected.%20Its%20infrastructure%20score%20of%2023.2%20out%20of%20100%20is%20the%20lowest%20in%20the%20index%2C%20thanks%20to%20Russian%20bombs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20shift%20towards%20normality%20after%20the%20pandemic%20has%20overall%20boded%20well%20for%20global%20liveability%20in%202023%2C%E2%80%9D%20Upasana%20Dutt%2C%20head%20of%20the%20liveability%20index%20at%20EIU%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%20%E2%80%9CEducation%20has%20emerged%20stronger%20with%20children%20returning%20to%20schools%2C%20alongside%20a%20significantly%20reduced%20burden%20on%20hospitals%20and%20healthcare%20systems%2C%20with%20some%20notable%20improvements%20in%20cities%20across%20developing%20economies%20of%20Asia%20and%20the%20Middle%20East.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20the%20world's%20political%20and%20economic%20axis%20continues%20to%20shift%20eastwards%2C%20we%20expect%20the%20cities%20in%20these%20regions%20to%20move%20slowly%20up%20our%20liveability%20rankings.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692006180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2018-03%2Fchennai-generic_650x400_41522244573.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fthese-are-most-liveable-cities-in-asia-pacific-how-do-indian-cities-rank-4295631%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20a%20global%20city%2C%20Singapore%20is%20no%20stranger%20to%20being%20on%20%26quot%3Bbest%26quot%3B%20lists.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fthese-are-most-liveable-cities-in-asia-pacific-how-do-indian-cities-rank-4295631%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fthese-are-most-liveable-cities-in-asia-pacific-how-do-indian-cities-rank-4295631%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fthese-are-most