0to%20Ban%20Intra-Gotra%2C%20Intra-Village%20Marriages%20as%20Per%20Khap%20Panchayats'%20Demands%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F14121527%2FF3T6TBIb0AAY7VK.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Haryana%20government%20has%20initiated%20the%20process%20of%20amending%20the%20%3Cem%3EHindu%20Marriage%20Act%2C%201955%3C%2Fem%3E%20(HMA)%20in%20response%20to%20khap%20panchayats%E2%80%99%20demands%20to%20ban%20intra-gotra%20and%20intra-village%20marriages%20as%20well%20as%20the%20registration%20of%20live-in%20relationships%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3ETribune%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tribuneindia.com%2Fnews%2Fharyana%2Fharyana-government-sets-in-motion-demand-of-khaps-for-amendment-in-hindu-marriage-act-534873%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20government%E2%80%99s%20Additional%20Chief%20Secretary%2C%20Home%20Department%2C%20referred%20the%20matter%20to%20the%20Principal%20Secretary%2C%20Citizen%20Resources%20Information%20Department%20(CRID)%20for%20further%20action%2C%20acting%20on%20the%20demands%20submitted%20by%20the%20Bharat%20Bhoomi%20Bachao%20Sangharsh%20Samiti%20president%20Ramesh%20Dalal%20and%20Sarvjatia%20Kandela%20Khap%20head%20Dharam%20Pal%20Kandela.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20report%2C%20Kandela%20said%20%E2%80%98same-gotra%20and%20same-village%20marriages%20were%20in%20conflict%20with%20the%20social%20norms%20in%20society%E2%80%99%20and%20they%20had%20submitted%20a%20representation%20to%20the%20state%20government%20for%20amendment%20of%20the%20HMA%20in%20line%20with%20the%20khap%20panchayats%E2%80%99%20demands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20intra-gotra%20and%20intra-village%20marriages%20amount%20to%20social%20stigma%2C%20which%20result%20in%20constant%20humiliation%20and%20mental%20torture%20of%20the%20parents%20whose%20boy%2Fgirl%20solemnise%20such%20marital%20ties%20which%20are%20in%20violation%20of%20social%20norms.%20It%20is%20necessary%20to%20bring%20amendments%20in%20the%20HMA%20to%20accommodate%20the%20conditions%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20social%20norms%20for%20maintaining%20the%20social%20fabric%20and%20a%20happy%20family%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kandela%20was%20quoted%20by%20the%20%3Cem%3ETribune%3C%2Fem%3E%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDalal%20had%20also%20submitted%20a%20representation%20to%20the%20state%20government%20last%20month%20with%20the%20demand%20that%20in%20addition%20to%20intra-gotra%20and%20intra-village%20marriages%2C%20those%20between%20people%20from%20bordering%20villages%20should%20also%20be%20declared%20invalid.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDalal%20said%20he%20was%20assured%20by%20top%20officials%20of%20the%20government%20that%20the%20matter%20had%20been%20assigned%20to%20a%20senior%20official%20who%20was%20likely%20to%20submit%20the%20final%20report%20to%20chief%20minister%20Manohar%20Lal%20Khattar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThereafter%2C%20the%20CM%20will%20take%20the%20final%20decision%20on%20the%20demand.%20In%20principle%2C%20the%20government%20was%20in%20agreement%20with%20me%20on%20the%20proposal%20for%20amendment%20in%20the%20HMA%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20was%20quoted%20by%20the%20paper%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20representation%20was%20submitted%20to%20the%20Haryana%20government%20on%20July%201%2C%20%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fcities%2Fchandigarh-news%2Fkhap-panchayats-in-haryana-demand-amendment-to-hindu-marriage-act-to-prohibit-same-gotra-marriages-101688410663798.html%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Nearly%20200%20%3Cem%3Emahapanchayats%3C%2Fem%3E%20have%20been%20organised%20by%20khap%20panchayats%20demanding%20the%20prohibition%20of%20such%20marriages%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691995982000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F14121527%2FF3T6TBIb0AAY7VK.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fharyana-govt-to-ban-intra-gotra-intra-village-marriages-as-per-khap-panchayats-demands%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Manohar%20Lal%20Khattar%20government%20has%20begun%20the%20process%20of%20amending%20the%20Hindu%20Marriage%20Act%2C%201955.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A55%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fharyana-govt-to-ban-intra-gotra-intra-village-marriages-as-per-khap-panchayats-demands%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20Elderly%20Citizens%20in%20India%20Are%20Finding%20Love%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F14085245%2FVillagers_from_india_16.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EMadhav%20Damle%20runs%20a%20home%20for%20senior%20citizens%20in%20Wai%2C%20a%20town%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Findia%2Ft-18996071%5C%22%3EIndia%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%98s%20western%20state%20of%20Maharashtra.%20Years%20ago%2C%20his%20job%20made%20him%20face%20an%20uncomfortable%20truth%20%E2%80%94%20many%20of%20the%20residents%20were%20experiencing%20loneliness%20and%20stress%2C%20and%20had%20poor%20relations%20with%20their%20families%20and%20friends.%20At%20least%20one%20of%20the%20seniors%20under%20his%20care%20tried%20to%20commit%20suicide%20by%20consuming%20sleeping%20pills.%20His%20adult%20children%20expressed%20little%20interest%20in%20taking%C2%A0care%20of%20him%2C%20said%20Damle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELooking%20for%20ways%20to%20ease%20his%20clients%E2%80%99%20isolation%2C%20Damle%20had%20an%20idea%20%E2%80%94%20he%20tried%20matching%20them%20into%20couples%20with%20a%20perspective%20of%20marriage.%20This%20worked%20especially%20well%20for%20clients%20in%20their%20mid%20to%20late%2060s.%20But%20he%20then%20faced%20an%20unexpected%20obstacle%2C%20as%20some%20of%20the%20clients%E2%80%99%20children%20disliked%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Findia-elderly-couple-sue-son-over-lack-of-grandchildren%2Fa-61768426%5C%22%3Eelderly%20relatives%3C%2Fa%3E%20marrying%2C%20due%20to%20inheritance%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20why%2C%20I%20thought%20live-in%20relationships%20might%20be%20a%20good%20solution%20for%20the%20couples.%20We%20conducted%20a%20survey%20among%20some%20seniors%20in%20%5Bthe%20Maharashtra%20city%20of%5D%20Pune%2C%20and%20about%2070%25%20of%20them%20were%20open%20to%20the%20idea%20of%20a%20live-in%20partner%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Time%20and%20love%E2%80%99%20as%20top%20priorities%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20society%20is%20remarkably%20conservative%20when%20it%C2%A0comes%20to%20marriage%20and%20relationships.%20The%20divorce%20rate%20in%20India%20is%20about%201%25%20%E2%80%94%20among%20the%20lowest%20in%20the%20world.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20there%20is%20a%20social%20stigma%20against%20remarrying%20and%20against%20unmarried%20couples%20living%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20issue%20has%20even%20made%20it%20to%20the%20Indian%20Supreme%20Court%20in%202006%2C%20with%20the%20judges%20finding%20that%20a%20%E2%80%9Clive-in%20relationship%20between%20two%20consenting%20adults%20of%20heterogenic%20sex%20does%20not%20amount%20to%20any%20offense%2C%20even%20though%20it%20may%20be%20perceived%20as%20immoral.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDamle%20officially%20started%20his%20matchmaking%20agency%20in%202012%2C%20which%20later%20came%20to%20be%20known%20as%20%E2%80%9CHappy%20Seniors.%E2%80%9D%20He%20is%20managing%20and%20sharing%20profiles%2C%20while%20also%20organizing%20meet-ups%20and%20trips%20for%20his%20clients.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENitin%20Savgave%20and%20Saroj%20Ghatani%20found%20each%20other%20through%20Damle.%20The%20two%20are%20now%20married.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20only%20requirement%20from%20a%20partner%20was%20their%20time%20and%20love.%20I%20got%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ghatani%20told%20DW.%20She%20added%20that%20her%20family%20did%20not%20approve%20of%20her%20new%20marriage%2C%20but%20this%20did%20not%20deter%20her%20and%C2%A0Savgave.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20enjoy%20each%20others%E2%80%99%20company%20and%20spend%20most%20of%20our%20time%20together%2C%E2%80%9D%C2%A0Ghatani%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESavgave%E2%80%99s%20family%20was%20more%20supportive.%20%E2%80%9CShe%20is%20vegetarian%2C%20whereas%20I%20eat%20meat%20frequently%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20we%20have%20adapted%20to%20each%20other%20and%20enjoy%20the%20companionship.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMinefield%20of%20dating%20apps%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Findianmatchmakingfraught-with-sexism-class-and-caste-issues%2Fa-55174165%5C%22%3EMatchmaking%20is%20a%20time-honored%20craft%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20India.%20But%20finding%20a%20partner%20online%20is%20growing%20increasingly%20common%2C%20and%20even%20some%20older%20Indians%20are%20turning%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fhow-indians-with-disabilities-find-love-through-dating-apps%2Fa-64784892%5C%22%3Emodern%20dating%20apps%20to%20find%20love%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETina%20(name%20changed)%2C%2064%2C%20decided%20to%20do%20just%20that%20after%20walking%20out%20of%20an%20abusive%20marriage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20got%20married%20at%2018%20and%20became%20a%20mum%20by%2020%2C%20I%20never%20got%20the%20chance%20to%20be%20myself.%C2%A0%20So%20after%20I%20split%2C%20I%20had%20all%20this%20freedom%20and%20no%20one%20to%20dictate%20my%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20told%20DW.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20while%2C%20she%20tried%20using%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fonline-dating%2Ft-38790642%5C%22%3Edating%20apps%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0in%20search%20of%20companionship.%20%E2%80%9CI%20found%20a%20lot%20of%20men%20were%20married%2C%20and%20looking%20to%20cheat%20on%20their%20wives.%20There%20were%20also%20some%20younger%20men%20looking%20for%20an%20older%20woman.%20I%20got%20fed%20up%20with%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20admitted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20her%20frustration%20eventually%20paid%20off.%20She%20found%20a%20partner%20through%20an%20app%2C%20and%20%E2%80%94%20after%20chatting%20for%20about%20five%20years%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0%20the%20two%20finally%20met.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%E2%80%99re%20both%20definitely%20not%20looking%20for%20marriage.%20Just%20companionship%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20children%20know%20about%20her%20relationship.%20Her%20partner%20also%20has%20one%20child%20and%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20acceptance%20has%20not%20been%20forthcoming%2C%E2%80%9D%20Tina%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMost%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20seniors%20lonely%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20breaking%20taboos%20is%20likely%20to%20grow%20increasingly%20common%20as%20both%20India%E2%80%99s%20society%20and%20its%20population%20shift.%20Today%2C%20about%205.7%25%20of%20Indian%20senior%20citizens%20live%20alone%20without%20the%20support%20of%20family%20or%20friends%2C%20according%20to%20a%20survey%20by%20India%E2%80%99s%20PAN%20Healthcare.%20It%20was%20conducted%20among%2010%2C000%20elderly%20population%20across%2010%20cities%20in%20India%2C%20and%20also%20found%20that%20a%20majority%20of%20responders%20feel%20lonely%20at%20least%20some%20of%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%2C%20with%20India%20now%20the%20most%20populous%20country%20in%20the%20word%2C%20the%20number%20of%20its%20seniors%20is%20climbing%20%E2%80%94%20the%20UN%20Population%20Fund%20said%20it%20will%20touch%20192%20million%20by%202030%2C%20and%2C%20by%202050%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fdemographics%2Ft-62940381%5C%22%3Eevery%20fifth%20Indian%20will%20be%20an%20elderly%20person%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20defined%20by%20the%20UN%20as%20aged%2060%20or%20older.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fhow-elderly-citizens-in-india-are-finding-love%2Fa-66504452%5C%22%3Earticle%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20originally%20published%20on%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%5C%22%3EDW%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691995559000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F14085245%2FVillagers_from_india_16.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsociety%2Fhow-elderly-citizens-in-india-are-finding-love%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22More%20and%20more%20Indian%20seniors%20are%20refusing%20to%20spend%20their%20twilight%20years%20alone%20and%20are%20turning%20to%20matchmaking%20and%20dating%20apps.%20But%20this%20means%20breaking%20some%20deep-seated%20taboos.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsociety%2Fhow-elderly-citizens-in-india-are-finding-love%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20Accurately%20Do%20We%20Measure%20Poverty%20in%20India%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F14120533%2F4882154176_e9f0324cee_c.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EA%20significant%20decline%20in%20poverty%20%E2%80%93%20this%20is%20what%20a%20recent%20NITI%20Aayog%20report%20announced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20data%20published%20showed%20that%20over%20a%20span%20of%20five%20years%2C%20about%2013.5%20crore%20Indians%20came%20out%20of%20poverty.%20In%20fact%2C%20this%20measure%20was%20of%20multidimensional%20poverty%2C%20therefore%20it%20seemed%20that%20on%20the%20whole%2C%20crores%20of%20people%20enjoyed%20the%20fruits%20of%20holistic%20progress.%20They%20are%20no%20longer%20below%20the%20poverty%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20does%20the%20methodology%20and%20its%20results%20hold%20up%20to%20closer%20examination%3F%20Has%20the%20%E2%80%98multidimensional%E2%80%99%20index%20been%20able%20to%20capture%20the%20full%20picture%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPerhaps%20not.%20To%20start%20with%2C%20the%20government%20of%20India%20has%20not%20been%20able%20to%20tell%20citizens%20the%20number%20and%20share%20of%20the%20population%20below%20the%20consumption%20poverty%20line%2C%20which%20has%20been%20the%20traditional%20method%20of%20estimating%20poverty%20globally%20for%20decades.%20India%20has%20used%20consumption%20poverty%20as%20the%20measure%20for%20over%20four%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20had%20not%20released%20a%20consumption%20expenditure%20survey%20conducted%20by%20the%20National%20Survey%20Organisation%20(NSO)%20in%202017-18.%20The%20NSO%20has%20announced%20consumption%20expenditure%20surveys%20for%202022-23%20and%202023-24.%20These%20might%20reveal%20to%20us%20what%20has%20happened%20to%20consumption%20(or%20money-metric)%20poverty%20in%20the%20last%2010%20years.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20NITI%20Aayog%20has%20just%20released%20the%20national%20multidimensional%20poverty%20index%20(MPI)%20for%20India%2C%20a%20few%20days%20after%20the%20global%20MPI%20estimates%20were%20released.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2010%20indicators%20of%20the%20global%20MPI%20are%20a%20mishmash%20of%20very%20different%20types%20of%20indicators.%20Some%20are%20indicators%20of%20inputs%2C%20others%20of%20process%2C%20yet%20others%20are%20output%20or%20outcome%20indicators.%20For%20instance%2C%20the%20education%20ones%20%E2%80%93%20having%20not%20completed%206%20years%20of%20school%20and%20children%20up%20to%20Class%208%20not%20attending%20school%20%E2%80%93%20are%20output%20and%20process%20indicators%2C%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20health%20ones%20are%20both%20outcome%20indicators%20%E2%80%93%20adult%20body%20mass%20index%20and%20child%20nutrition.%20All%20six%20indicators%20of%20standard%20of%20living%20are%20input-based%20%E2%80%93%20electricity%2C%20drinking%20water%2C%20sanitation%2C%20cooking%20fuel%2C%20home%20floor%20and%20consumer%20assets.%20In%20statistics%2C%20it%20is%20theoretically%20flawed%20to%20lump%20together%20such%20different%20indicators%20to%20construct%20an%20index.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENational%20and%20global%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20this%2C%20the%20national%20MPI%20(NMPI)%20indicator%20framework%20has%20been%20modified%20vis-%C3%A0-vis%20global%20MPI%20and%20interestingly%2C%20no%20reason%20has%20been%20provided%20in%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NMPI%20framework%20has%2012%20instead%20of%2010%20globally%20considered%20indicators.%20The%20two%20new%20indicators%20are%3A%20Maternal%20health%20in%20the%20%E2%80%98health%E2%80%99%20dimension%20and%20access%20to%20banking%20in%20the%20%E2%80%98standards%20of%20living%E2%80%99%20dimension.%20This%20addition%20leads%20to%20change%20in%20the%20weights%20assigned%20to%20the%20two%20indicators%2C%20which%20were%20the%20two%20high-contributing%20factors%20to%20poverty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20global%20MPI%202022%20report%2C%20released%20a%20few%20weeks%20ago%2C%20had%20reported%20that%20India%20had%20reduced%20its%20incidence%20of%20multidimensional%20poverty%20from%2054%25%20in%202005-06%20(National%20Family%20Health%20Survey%203)%20to%2027.9%25%20of%20the%20total%20population%20in%202015-16%20(NFHS%204)%2C%20halving%20the%20head%20count%20ratio.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECompared%20to%20that%2C%20the%20global%20MPI%20reported%20that%20the%20reduction%20in%20multidimensional%20poverty%20between%202015-16%20was%20from%2027.9%25%20to%2016%25%20in%202019-21%20(NFHS%205).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fks-james-nfhs-modi-government-data-sets-iips%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Unhappy%20With%20Data%20Sets%2C%E2%80%99%20Modi%20Govt%20Suspends%20Director%20of%20Institute%20Which%20Prepares%20NFHS%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EExcluding%20millions%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20the%20global%20nutrition%20indicator%20was%20modified%20in%20NMPI%2C%20leaving%20out%20children%20aged%20six%20to%2014%20years%2C%20consisting%20of%20more%20than%2018%25%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20population.%20More%20than%20two-third%20of%20this%20population%20group%20suffers%20from%20anemia.%20NMPI%20thus%20leaves%20many%20poor%20and%20deprived%20out%20of%20the%20count%20on%20this%20account.%20More%20importantly%2C%20the%20NMPI%20uses%20undernourishment%20of%20under-fives%20(weight%20for%20age)%2C%20while%20the%20global%20MPI%20uses%20a%20more%20robust%20indicator%20%E2%80%93%20stunting%20(height%20for%20age).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20latter%20is%20higher%20(35.5%25%20in%20NFHS%205)%20in%20India%20than%20the%20underweight%20measure%20(31.1%25%20in%20NFHS%205).%20Worse%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20stunting%20rate%20is%20higher%20than%20that%20of%20Sub-saharan%20Africa%20(32%25)%3B%20just%20as%20India%E2%80%99s%20child%20wasting%20rate%20is%2019.1%25%20(NFHS%205)%2C%20while%20Africa%E2%80%99s%20is%206%25%20(UNICEF%2C%202023%2C%20State%20of%20World%E2%80%99s%20Children).%20Moreover%2C%20the%20recently%20released%20%E2%80%98The%20State%20of%20Food%20Security%20and%20Nutrition%20in%20the%20World%202023%E2%80%99%20report%20by%20the%20UN%20highlighted%20that%20104.3%20crore%20(74.1%25)%20Indians%20are%20unable%20to%20afford%20healthy%20food.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESecondly%2C%20selection%20of%20the%20new%20indicator%20on%20maternal%20health%20is%20faulty.%20It%20regards%20a%20pregnant%20woman%20to%20be%20deprived%20if%20her%20delivery%20is%20executed%20by%20an%20unskilled%20health%20personnel%20or%20if%20she%20has%20not%20availed%20the%20prescribed%20four%20antenatal%20care%20services.%20Most%20deliveries%20(more%20than%2080%25)%20are%20now%20happening%20in%20a%20health%20institution.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20there%20are%20very%20few%20deprived%20on%20this%20indicator.%20This%20will%20tend%20to%20significantly%20reduce%20the%20count%20of%20deprived%20pregnant%20women%2C%20reducing%20the%20overall%20number%20of%20persons%20falling%20under%20the%20category%20of%20multidimensionally%20poor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThirdly%2C%20take%20the%20issue%20of%20the%20addition%20of%20a%20new%20indicator%20%E2%80%93%20%E2%80%98No%20household%20member%20has%20a%20bank%20account%20or%20a%20post%20office%20account%E2%80%99%20in%20the%20standard%20of%20living%20dimension.%20As%20per%20NFHS%204%2C%20nine%20out%20of%2010%20persons%20in%20the%20country%20(90.3%25)%20had%20either%20a%20bank%20account%20and%2For%20a%20post%20office%20account.%20While%20this%20is%20a%20major%20achievement%20for%20computation%20of%20deprivation%20and%20policy%20purposes%2C%20inclusion%20of%20this%20indicator%20significantly%20influences%20the%20overall%20number%20of%20deprived%20persons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDiffering%20data%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20and%20most%20worrying%20is%20the%20following%3A%20The%20MPI%20estimate%20for%20multidimensionally%20poor%20people%20in%20India%20in%202019-21%20estimates%20reduction%20from%20the%202015-16%20figure.%20The%20NITI%20Aayog%E2%80%99s%20report%20estimates%20the%20number%20of%20people%20rising%20out%20of%20poverty%20to%20be%20135%20million.%20However%2C%20there%20is%20a%20sleight%20of%20hand%20in%20the%20NITI%20Aayog%20estimate.%20I%20double%20checked%20the%20projected%20population%20used%20for%202015-16%20and%20for%202019-21%20as%20a%20denominator%20for%20determining%20the%20absolute%20number%20of%20MPI%20poor%20in%20each%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EObviously%2C%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20exact%20population%20data%20between%20census%20years%2C%20we%20use%20population%20projections%2C%20as%20provided%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Health%20and%20Family%20Welfare%2C%20based%20on%20Census%202011.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENaturally%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20projected%20population%20in%202021%20will%20be%20higher%20than%20that%20in%202015-16.%20To%20arrive%20at%20the%20number%20of%20MPI%20poor%20for%202021%2C%20that%20year%E2%80%99s%20population%20should%20be%20used%3B%20and%20to%20arrive%20at%20the%20number%20of%20MPI%20poor%20for%202015-16%2C%20again%20the%20latter%20year%E2%80%99s%20population%20should%20be%20used.%20If%2C%20on%20the%20one%20hand%2C%C2%A0%20someone%20uses%20the%20same%20estimate%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20total%20population%20for%20both%20years%2C%20the%20number%20of%20people%20pulled%20out%20of%20MPI%20poverty%20will%20be%20overstated.%20That%20is%20exactly%20what%20I%20found%20the%20NITI%20Aayog%20has%20done.%20The%20estimated%20population%20for%20both%20years%20was%20found%20to%20be%20the%20same.%20The%20result%20is%20that%20the%20NITI%20Aayog%20is%20claiming%20that%20India%20pulled%20135%20million%20out%20of%20MPI%20poverty%2C%20when%20in%20fact%20that%20number%20is%20really%20around%20118%20million%20(because%20the%20total%20population%20of%20India%20in%202015%20was%20naturally%20lower%20than%20in%202021).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20even%20if%20one%20goes%20by%20the%20NMPI%20estimates%20for%202019-21%20and%20projects%20it%20onto%20the%202021%20estimated%20population%2C%20410%20million%20people%20are%20still%20deprived%20on%20the%20sanitation%20indicator%20of%20NMPI.%20Yet%2C%20the%20government%20has%20claimed%20that%20India%20has%20become%20open%20defecation%20free.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20unfortunate%20that%20government%20estimates%20fail%20to%20paint%20an%20accurate%20picture%20of%20the%20realities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESantosh%20Mehrotra%20was%20the%20chief%20economist%20of%20the%20global%20Human%20Development%20Report%20(2002-04)%2C%20UNDP%20New%20York%2C%20and%20the%20lead%20author%20of%20the%20second%20India%20Human%20Development%20Report%20(OUP%2C%202011)%20of%20the%20Planning%20Commission%20of%20India.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20first%20appeared%20on%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Fhow-are-we-defining-and-measuring-poverty-in-india-2645724%5C%22%3EDeccan%20Herald%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20and%20has%20been%20republished%20with%20permission.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%