%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F179905%2Findia-new-education-preschool-primary-curriculum-startup%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERote%20learning%20%3C%2Fa%3Eis%20itself%20a%20dangerous%20thing%2C%20it%20imparts%20no%20skills%20to%20students.%20It%20is%20a%20very%20rigid%20architecture%20psychologically.%20As%20a%20teacher%2C%20your%20job%20is%20to%20manage%20a%20classroom%20of%20100%20students%2C%20it%20is%20not%20about%20teaching%20them%2C%20just%20handling%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20our%20classrooms%2C%20the%20person%20who%20sits%20in%20the%20back%20row%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20a%20clown.%20Others%20do%20not%20collaborate%20with%20them.%20Whenever%20a%20backbencher%20stands%20up%2C%20everyone%20bursts%20into%20laughter%2C%20that%20student%20starts%20thinking%20they%20are%20a%20%E2%80%98joker%E2%80%99%20and%20they%20lose%20the%20confidence%20to%20do%20better%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20experiences%20led%20Rennis%20and%20Imma%20(whom%20he%20met%20in%20JNU)%20to%20start%20Ignis%20Careers%20in%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fignis-careers-1-1691584690.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rennis%20and%20his%20team%20have%20taught%20English%20language%20and%20life%20skills%20to%20over%203.5%20lakh%20students%20in%20about%201%2C000%20low-cost%20schools.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fignis-careers-1-1691584690.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fignis-careers-1-1691584690-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fignis-careers-1-1691584690-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20http