-builds-ai-enabled-gardening-robot-for-all-ages-to-remove-weeds%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98I%20Rescued%20a%20Cobra%20at%2016%E2%80%99%3A%20Chennai%E2%80%99s%2024-YO%20Has%20Rescued%206000%20Snakes%20in%209%20Years%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhen%20Vedhapriya%20Ganesan%20was%20just%20three%20years%20old%2C%20she%20found%20a%20newborn%20shrew%20(%3Cem%3Emoonjur%20eli%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20Tamil)%20behind%20her%20%3Cem%3Eanganwadi%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20the%20mother%20was%20missing.%20Disturbed%20by%20the%20animal%E2%80%99s%20plight%2C%20she%20found%20a%20tailor%20nearby%20and%20asked%20him%20to%20stitch%20a%20small%20swing%20for%20the%20animal.%20Then%2C%20she%20rocked%20him%20in%20it%20like%20one%20would%20a%20human%20baby!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEvery%20day%2C%20I%20would%20go%20and%20see%20the%20%3Cem%3Emoonjur%20%3C%2Fem%3Eto%20ensure%20it%20was%20doing%20well%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20was%20Vedhapriya%E2%80%99s%20beginning%20of%20a%20lifelong%20tryst%20with%20animals.%20As%20she%20grew%20older%2C%20her%20love%20for%20animals%20grew%20into%20compassion%20and%20a%20need%20to%20protect%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20school%20trip%20to%20the%20snake%20park%20ignited%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F298187%2Fbihar-snake-man-fights-superstition-to-rescue-snakes-sets-up-animal-centre%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epassion%20for%20snakes%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20this%20now%2024-year-old%20woman.%20%E2%80%9CThat%20was%20my%20first%20trip%20to%20the%20snake%20park.%20We%20were%20taught%20about%20different%20species%20of%20snakes%20by%20Dr%20S%20R%20Ganesh%2C%20who%20is%20a%20herpetologist.%20I%20found%20his%20talk%20fascinating%2C%20and%20the%20reptiles%2C%20even%20more%20so%2C%E2%80%9D%20Vedhapriya%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20resident%20of%20C