-bsf-indo-pak-war%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecamel%20herders%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20helps%20at%20least%2045%2C000%20camels%20thrive%20by%20selling%20camel%20milk-based%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CCan%20you%20imagine%20deserts%20without%20camels%3F%20We%20attempt%20to%20bring%20livelihood%20opportunities%20to%20these%20communities%2C%20highly%20nutritious%20food%20for%20our%20customers%2C%20as%20well%20as%20bring%20the%20cause%20of%20camel%20conservation%20through%20these%20products%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EJournalist%20turned%20entrepreneur%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202017%2C%20Aakriti%20moved%20to%20Bajju%20village%20in%20Bikaner%20district%20near%20the%20India-Pakistan%20border%2C%20nearly%201%2C200%20km%20from%20her%20hometown%20in%20UP%E2%80%99s%20Gorakhpur.%20It%20was%20while%20pursuing%20her%20graduation%20in%20journalism%20and%20mass%20communication%20in%20Delhi%20that%20she%20was%20assigned%20to%20document%20stories%20of%20pastoralists%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F325795%2Fretired-army-officer-colonel-mahendra-mohan-oasis-luxury-camps-in-jaisalmer%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThar%20desert%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20went%20to%20the%20desert%20in%20June.%20All%20my%20romantic%20notions%20of%20what%20a%20desert%20would%20be%20like%20were%20shattered%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20her%20first%20visit%20which%20was%20for%20four%20months%2C%20she%20learnt%20about%20the%20community%20of%20pastoralists%2C%20camel%20herders%2C%20sheep%20goat%20rearers%2C%20and%20indigenous%20cow%20rearers.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20challenging%20geographies%20and%20extreme%20temperatures%2C%20these%20communities%20would%20travel%20eight%20months%20on%20foot%20covering%20800%20km%20of%20stretch%20with%20their%20herds%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPasto